A DevTeach Winner! Week 5, The Art of Computer Programming Boxed Set!

Posted by Brendan Tompkins on October 12, 2011

Congratulations to our week 4 CodeBetter Fantasy Football winner, Kasi Prasad with 79 points! Kasi and two of his friends will be going to  DevTeach Ottawa!

Next  week, we’re giving away The Art of Computer Programming, Volumes 1-4A Boxed Set, The, 3rd Edition

The bible of all fundamental algorithms and the work that taught many of today’s software developers most of what they know about computer programming.

—Byte, September 1995

What do I have to do to enter?

Not much!  All you need to do is comment/trackback/tweet this and you’re eligible.  We’ll pick a winner and announce the final recipient next week after all games have been played.
